rows.label: qst000401_msg0003
rows.name:
I wanna play with 'em too!
Except I can't swim...

rows.label: qst000401_msg0004
rows.name:
So when everyone's havin' fun at the
waterside, I just stand here feeling daft.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0005
rows.name:
I'd like to practice my swimming,
but without the equipment I need,
it's all a bit tough.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0006
rows.name:
I heard about a plant that grows on
Coolley Lake, called Buoyweed.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0007
rows.name:
It floats on water, so it'd be perfect
for swimming lessons, but...

rows.label: qst000401_msg0008
rows.name:
There's monsters near where
Buoyweed grows, so I can't just pick it.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0009
rows.name: I nearly got ate last time I tried...

rows.label: qst000401_msg0011
rows.name:
Well, three of them should be enough
to keep me afloat.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0013
rows.name:
I saw the Buoyweed around the middle
of Coolley Lake last time.

rows.label: qst000401_msg0014
rows.name: Lemme know once you get three!
